    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. This is an investment-grade example of engineering mastery, offered for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
